@NODE history " Program history"

Version 1.0   - Initial release.

Version 1.1   - Added ability to twit users automatically (Requires
                Blitz-Twit)
              - Now rounds the expiry time to 0:00 the day after the
                membership expires.
              - Added 6 sort options to list output.
              - Added switch for report sorting.
              - Added -M switch.
              - Decided to make BMM shareware
              - MB capacity listing in report is now optional.
              - Users can now access the database and list other members.

Version 1.2   - Fixed a bug in MB capacity output.
              - Fixed allignment of report file output.
              - Now displays the date the user's membership will expire.
              - Added page pausing to listing when outputting to screen.
              - When run on-line, can now do more than one listing at a time.
              - Fixed spelling mistake of 'Expiery'!
              - Added RECEIPT parameter.
              - Moved all data files to 'DOORS:BMM/'

Version 1.3   - Fixed a severe bug when editing a user.
              - Pressing <RETURN> at edit prompt now returns to main menu.
              - Now correctly identifies unlimited license keyfile.
              - Added B menu option to config menu.
              - Added 'Hunt' mode to days remaining.
              - Now goes to edit menu if a new member already exists in the
                database.

@ENDNODE
